      "text": "Long ago a Gandharva used to come daily for darshanam — at Thiruvanchikulam for the deeparadhana, at the Urakam temple for the night seeveli, and at the Thrissivaperur Vadakkunnatha temple for the thrippuka.",
      "units": [],
      "relation": "interpretive"
